# Workspace guidance precedence

1. **`.cursor/rules`** — follow these first.
2. **`AGENTS.md`**, **`CLAUDE.md`**, **`TOOLS.md`**, and other documentation in this repo.

Use external rule systems **only when the user explicitly requests** them. Do not auto-fetch or treat them as the default for normal Cursor work.
